Prince Albert's 42 grandchildren included four reigning monarchs: [[George V|King George V of the United Kingdom]]; [[Wilhelm II, German Emperor]]; [[Ernest Louis, Grand Duke of Hesse]]; and [[Charles Edward, Duke of Saxe-Coburg and Gotha]]. Albert's many descendants include royalty and nobility throughout Europe.

